":guilabel:`Recurring Plans` dashboard, to reveal a blank form where the plan"
" :guilabel:`Name`, :guilabel:`DETAILS`, :guilabel:`SELF-SERVICE` and "
":guilabel:`Pricing` field values are specified."
msgstr ""
